reviewText:
I am in school,
I needed a short DVD
to get my point across about
this Hotel and it was exactly
What I wanted. Many details.

In twenty-first century we have a wonderful new destination: Dubai. Everything you read and observe the images on TV are little compared to the fantastic reality. Buildings, highways, shopping centers surprised eyes of the visitor. In this video, you are transported to this magical city. Try to realize their dreams and enjoy your life.
German Bernate
